<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.4.8">
<l>nīla malarkaḷ neṭunīr vayalmaruṅkil</l>
<l>cāla malarellā mūtātē vāḷarakkar</l>
<l>kālaṉkaṇ ṇapurattem perumāṉ katirmuṭimēl</l>
<l>kōla naṟuntuḻāy koṇṭūtāy kōltumpī.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without sipping from the blue lotus blossoms</l>
<l>And the entire multitude of flowers at the side of the wide, watered fields,</l>
<l>Twiggy dragonfly, clasp and sip the beautiful, fragrant tulasī</l>
<l>On the shining crown our great lord of Kaṇṇapuram,</l>
<l rend="indent">death to the sword demon.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
